Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ada tugas untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.81,0:09:29.98,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Ini tempatnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:35.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ya. Dengan dandanan ini{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.24,0:09:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}aku terlihat seperti reporter!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.03,0:09:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ada tugas untukmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.33,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak peduli apa itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.62,0:09:47.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku perlu kau cari tahu lebih banyak\Ntentang para pembalap luar negeri ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.21,0:09:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.54,0:09:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bersikaplah sebijaksana mungkin.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.59,0:09:54.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama-tama...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.97,0:10:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Halo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Moonlight Lunacy, mewakili Inggris.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.56,0:10:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Juara kelima di Piala Jepang tahun lalu.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.19,0:10:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Menurutnya,\Nbalapan di depan berjalan buruk,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.24,0:10:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}jadi dia mungkin akan mengubah strategi.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.95,0:10:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Di tempat asalnya, dia biasa\Nmenjadi pelari tengah atau pelari akhir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.70,0:10:26.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Piala Jepang tahun lalu\Ntampaknya seperti pengecualian.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.58,0:10:29.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia balapan di Prancis,\Ndengan rumput lebih lembut dari di Jepang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.62,0:10:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Karena itu, kukira larinya akan fokus\Nke kekuatan, tapi ternyata dia cepat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tampaknya dia dulu\Njuga menang melawan Toni Bianca.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Michelle My Baby, mewakili Amerika.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.97,0:10:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tinggi sekali, 195 cm.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dikenal punya kekuatan luar biasa\Nseperti buldoser.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.43,0:10:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Larinya yang nekat bermodal nyali\Nmengingatkanku pada Oguri?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.61,0:10:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia membangun kekuatannya bertahun-tahun\Ndan memenangkan lomba besar di Amerika.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.57,0:11:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Seperti pembalap Amerika lainnya,\Nkecepatannya terasa dinamis.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia dan timnya sangat percaya diri,\Nnyaris berlebihan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.75,0:11:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ellerslie Pride, mewakili Selandia Baru.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.37,0:11:15.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Juara Oseania dengan 18 kemenangan\Ndari 37 balapan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.21,0:11:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia memakai berbagai gaya lari dan\Ndikenal tak menyerah di bawah tekanan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.09,0:11:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia juga mampu mempertahankan\Nsprint terakhirnya untuk waktu yang lama.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sebaiknya awasi dia\Nsaat mencapai tikungan keempat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.26,0:11:31.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tahun lalu dia juga ke Jepang,\Ntapi harus mundur karena sakit.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.35,0:11:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia tampak bersemangat\Nuntuk menunjukkan kemampuannya kali ini.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.32,0:11:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Favorit di antara\Npembalap internasional, Toni Bianca.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.61,0:11:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia pemanasan ringan dan olahraga ringan\Nhari ini, tapi melihat langkahnya{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}yang panjang itu sungguh menonjol!\NPantas saja dia menjadi Penguasa Eropa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.37,0:11:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sebaiknya awasi dia.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.76,0:12:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Itulah empat besar\Ndi antara pembalap internasional...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku punya info tentang pembalap lain\Nuntuk jaga-jaga,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}tapi tampaknya hanya gadis ini\Nyang tak bisa kutemukan...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.65,0:12:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sungguh, di mana dia?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.71,0:12:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.34,0:12:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bagus sekali!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.92,0:12:45.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Obey Your Master?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.18,0:12:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Pembalap Amerika\Ndan yang terakhir di daftarku!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.26,0:12:53.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tunggu, berapa banyak\Nkemenangan G1 yang dia miliki?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.68,0:12:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Nol?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.52,0:13:02.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo! Obey Your Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.99,0:13:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang mewawancarai para pelari.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.78,0:13:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh aku beri beberapa pertanyaan padamu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.91,0:13:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Reporter yang cantik sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau mau mengobrol? Ayo mengobrol!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia bisa bicara bahasa Jepang.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana rumput di Jepang\Ndibandingkan di Amerika?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.92,0:13:21.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dibandingkan Amerika, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, seperti...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.22,0:13:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baunya sungguh luar biasa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baunya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.89,0:13:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari risetku, kau paling mahir\Ndi lomba jarak 2.000 meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.23,0:13:39.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana persiapanmu untuk\NArena Balap Tokyo sepanjang 2.400 meter?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.57,0:13:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu, sungguh melelahkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.23,0:13:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Ya, aku tak bisa lakukan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.57,0:13:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku harus pergi sebelum salah bicara\Ndan ungkap penyamaranku.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.95,0:13:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas waktumu.\NAku pergi sekarang...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:56.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami para tamu bukan satu-satunya\Nyang harus khawatir soal karakter treknya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:03.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jarak terpanjang yang pernah dia tempuh\Nhingga saat ini adalah 2.000 meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Timnya pasti khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.30,0:14:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pasti itu sebabnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.14,0:14:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau di luar sini menjadi mata-mata,\NBelno Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.60,0:14:19.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau haruskah kupanggil James Bond?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.19,0:14:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa kau tahu namaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.90,0:14:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya kenapa lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.28,0:14:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, temanmu sudah\Nmengubah gayanya sejak Kasamatsu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.41,0:14:32.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa Musaka memang seniman sejati.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.66,0:14:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sprint terakhir di Fall Tenno Sho itu\Nsungguh hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biar kuberi tahu sebuah rahasia kecil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.25,0:14:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya tiga musuh di balapan ini...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.75,0:14:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Toni,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.34,0:14:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tamamo,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.30,0:14:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan tentu saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.47,0:14:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Beri tahu Oguri Cap.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.64,0:14:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita pegangan tangan\Ndan melewati garis finis bersama-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.40,0:15:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bahkan tahu tentang\Nsaat Oguri di Kasamatsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.32,0:15:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya... Jelas dia benar-benar mendalami Oguri.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.49,0:15:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari yang terlihat, semua rival\Nluar negeri kita akan menyulitkan,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.08,0:15:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi sepertinya Obey Your Master ini\Npatut diwaspadai.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.71,0:15:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih.\NBoleh kupinjam buku catatanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.51,0:15:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Silakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.72,0:15:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Piala Jepang diadakan\Ndi Arena Balap Tokyo 2.400 meter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.90,0:15:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tapi...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:50.61,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Jarak terpanjang yang pernah dia tempuh
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.23,0:15:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hingga saat ini adalah 2.000 meter.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.69,0:15:52.45,Default Above,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\an8}Timnya pasti khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.36,0:15:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia benar-benar mengerjakan PR-nya...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.16,0:16:01.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia harus latihan dengan rekan lebih lagi\Nuntuk menyempurnakan strategi,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.75,0:16:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}tapi tetap di tim kami mungkin akan\Nmembuatnya punya kebiasaan buruk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Mungkin aku bisa minta bantuannya...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.11,0:16:32.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.32,0:16:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kerja bagus hari ini, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.45,0:16:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau lebih lama lagi,\Nkau bisa masuk angin, kita akhiri saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.30,0:16:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, cukup bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.63,0:16:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kau hebat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.55,0:17:00.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu kau bisa, Tama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.89,0:17:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau terus menjadi lebih baik\Nsampai hari besar itu tiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.18,0:17:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Hentikan!\NAku bisa mengeringkan diriku!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.31,0:17:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu yang kau katakan lima menit yang lalu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.07,0:17:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berlebihan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.49,0:17:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tukang khawatir, Komi.\NKau ini apa, ibuku?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.54,0:17:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.75,0:17:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tak perlu khawatir.\NAku masih bisa lari jauh!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.25,0:17:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah Tenno Sho,\Naku tahu aku bisa menang.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.38,0:17:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kaki ini tak akan kalah,\Ntidak pada dunia sekali pun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.68,0:17:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menjadi yang terbaik di Jepang,\Nselanjutnya di dunia!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.76,0:17:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat menang Arima Kinen,\Nnamaku akan tercatat dalam sejarah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.94,0:17:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama aku bisa melakukannya...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.03,0:17:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf, aku akan lari satu lap lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tama?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hari lain untuk joging ringan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.38,0:18:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia belum pernah berlatih dengan keras\Nsekali pun sejak datang ke Jepang.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.47,0:18:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa dia baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.88,0:18:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayolah, kau lihat langkahnya?\NDia pasti lawan terberat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.02,0:18:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halaman utama\Npasti menjadi milik Toni Bianca!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.77,0:18:33.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tidak buruk.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.19,0:18:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kekuatan dalam diriku mengalir kuat.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.57,0:18:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku bisa tahu hanya dengan joging ringan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Kondisiku sebaik sebelum\Nperjalananku ke sini, mungkin lebih baik!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.29,0:18:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Piala Jepang dalam tiga hari...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.92,0:18:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Sebentar lagi seluruh dunia\Nakan menjadi saksi karya besarku.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.59,0:19:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}36,5 detik! 12,4 detik!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.31,0:19:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf soal ini, Gold City.\NAku tahu permintaanku ini mendadak.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.98,0:19:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak masalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.77,0:20:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadinya kupikir aku perlu teman berlari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.95,0:20:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Aku anggap ini seperti balapan asli,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.91,0:20:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}tapi tetap saja...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.45,0:20:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tampaknya pemula ini\Nberlari sesuai harapan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.50,0:20:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}City, kau juga akan ikut Piala Jepang, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.83,0:20:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.38,0:20:19.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mengerti...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.76,0:20:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita lakukan yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, kupikir kita berdua akan bertarung.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.73,0:20:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali kau tak akan mengalahkanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semuanya baik?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.86,0:20:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada sesuatu yang kupikirkan\Nsejak aku lari di belakangmu...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.03,0:20:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.37,0:20:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pakai sampo apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rambutku sudah cukup panjang\Ndan terus tersangkut ke sesuatu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.51,0:21:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rambutmu juga panjang,\Ntapi terlihat sangat halus...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.64,0:21:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lain kali aku bawakan satu botol.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.69,0:21:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sungguh? Terima kasih!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sumpah, rambutku terus tersangkut\Napa pun yang kulakukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.48,0:21:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Itu bisa terjadi\Nkalau kau pakai sampo yang salah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.11,0:21:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, itu sangat sakit saat ditarik...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.78,0:21:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seburuk itu, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.62,0:21:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau kuberi perawatan rambut?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.12,0:21:31.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tunggu, sungguh?\N- Tentu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.88,0:21:45.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia memperkecil jarak!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.51,0:21:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tiga langkah, tidak, dua langkah lagi!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.89,0:21:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Bisakah dia mengejar Tamamo Cross?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.01,0:21:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Dia tak bisa!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.02,0:21:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Tamamo Cross mengebut,\Nmempertahankan keunggulannya!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.27,0:22:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Hanya satu langkah tersisa\Nantara Tamamo Cross dan Oguri Cap!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.52,0:22:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Apa Tamamo Cross sudah tamat?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.16,0:23:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}{\i1}Selanjutnya di{\i0} Umamusume: Cinderella Gray!
